com.hybris.cis.cybersource.avs.mapping

Class CsAvsStatusAndErrorFieldMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hybris.cis.cybersource.avs.mapping.CsAvsStatusAndErrorFieldMapping

  • public class CsAvsStatusAndErrorFieldMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    Field mapping for CyberSource status and error codes. Because CyberSource returns different codes depending on the country, we need different implementations (ugh!) See http://apps.cybersource.com/library/documentation/dev_guides/Verification_Svcs_IG/Verification_IG.pdf
